data.description: ACTIVE UNDER CONTRACT - ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS  INVESTOR SPECIAL  , Owner Motivated.... If you need room to grow this is the home for you. 4/4/3 pool home with over 3300 square feet under roof.  In addition to 4 bedrooms there is 2 offices, or they could be workout rooms etc. The Kitchen has beautiful granite countertops with a breakfast bar and a built-in desk. The eat in Kitchen overlooks the large family room with large windows to let the Florida sunlight in. The Master suite features a double vanity and garden tub for long, relaxing soaks. Master bath also includes sperate shower and walk in closets. Inside laundry, Formal Living room, Roof is 8 years old. This home has plenty of space and options to make your personal living needs possible. Silverthorn has many amenities including Tennis courts, pickle ball courts, Community pool, playground, Gated entrance and security, Golf Course, pro shop and Restaurant with amazing entertainment and menu. Minutes from the Suncoast Parkway and shopping, Family Restaurants and Fine dining, Parks and the Gulf of Mexico.
